It is not because the DN fails, it is due to that the client / pipeline put this DN into excludeNode list. So it then adds a DN to help for pipeline recover., Discussed with [~eddyxu], the concurrent write may be interrupted after the volume is removed, so client will then exclude that DataNode, therefore 3 DataNodes are not sufficient.

